message: Let's start fair. I'll take most of the money, but you get a decent cut. What do you say?
Alice, your offer was quite cheeky! Let's be reasonable. I'm proposing a 65/35 split in my favor.  Time is money, and it's losing value for both of us.
Okay, Bob, I'm willing to compromise. I'll take 40% and you take 60%. Let's get this over with. Time is indeed money, but it seems you value it more than I do.
